This Mutator will 'Replace' your current S.P. Musket with an enhanced version, featuring:

- New Enhanced scope/zoom that works like the M99, with new texture
[strike]
- Slight increase to the base damage
- Slight increase in reload speed
- Slight increase in aim speed
- Slight increase in weapon ammo capacity
- Slight decrease in cost
- Slight decrease in weight
[/strike]
Removed all buffs as of v2.0

[h1][b]Number Of Files[/b][/h1]

3

[h1][b]File Names[/b][/h1]

\System\KFEnhancedMusket.u
\System\KFEnhancedMusket.ucl

\Textures\KF_Enhanced_Musket_Scope.utx

[h1][b]Usage[/b][/h1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[h1][b]Mutators[/b][/h1]

There are 2 mutators. One will [b]spawn[/b] you with the weapon, and the other will [b]add it to the trader[/b] where you can buy it normally

[h1][b]Class Names[/b][/h1]

- Trader Shop Mut: KFEnhancedMusket.EnhancedMusketShopMut

- Spawn Mut: KFEnhancedMusket.KFEnhancedMusket

- ServerPerks Pickup Name: KFEnhancedMusket.EnhancedMusketPickup

[h1][b]Known Bugs (Will fix in later releases)[/b][/h1]

If you are using '[i]Low[/i]' or '[i]High[/i]' textures for the Scope settings, the scope will not work properly.

To fix this simply go to:

- Settings
- Check Advanced
- Switch scope settings to 'Textured'
- Done!

[h1][b]Manual Download Links (Recommended)[/b][/h1]

You can find it under 'Not Whitelisted' folder named KFEnhancedMusket-v2.0

